    "|-------|---------------|--------|\n",
    "| GPT-4o | 0.65-0.75 | Strong sustained attention |\n",
    "| Claude Sonnet | 0.60-0.70 | Good sustained (3-5 items) |\n",
    "| Gemini Pro | 0.55-0.65 | Moderate (8-13 items) |\n",
