    "### Context Length vs Performance\n",
    "\n",
    "Expected performance degradation:\n",
    "- Length 3: 85% accuracy\n",
    "- Length 5: 75% accuracy\n",
    "- Length 8: 65% accuracy\n",
    "- Length 13: 55% accuracy\n",
    "- Length 21: 45% accuracy"
